Subject: RE: [VB] How to clean out shift rod tube?

Fray a clutch cable and attach to a drill, thats how I do all the tubes in
my buses. After done blown out etc. I saturate in rust mort then leave
alone. I do not grease any of the tubes in my buses.

ronnie

